Package: porta
Version: __VERSION__
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.34)
Maintainer: Ekorau LLC <david@ekorau.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/davidg238/porta
Description: porta - northbound LAN gateway / node manager
 porta is a language-neutral, always-on LAN node manager. It owns the wire
 protocol, queues commands, delivers container images over TFTP, and ingests
 telemetry. UDP/TFTP listener on :6969; HTTP operator surface (control API +
 htmx console + read-only MCP) on :6970. State persists in /var/lib/porta.
